reviewText: ON A TRIP TO VEGAS, TWO FRIENDS ARE BOUND FOR THE STRIP WHERE BRIAN IS TO MEET HIS BRIDE. HIS BEST MAN ZACK WANTS HIM TO FULFILL HIS SEXUAL FANTASIES FIRST. SATISFACTION IS GUARANTEED AS THEY MEET BEAUTIFUL QUEENS. STRIPPERS AND WOMEN WHO ARE OUT OF THIS WORLD AND CAPABLE OF GRANTING THEIR EVERY WISH. WILL THEY REACH THE ALTER BEFORE THE WOMEN FIND A WAY TO SATISFY THEIR DESIRES BEFORE THE WEDDING?
